Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.54,0:00:07.12,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, buddy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.20,0:00:08.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:11.01,Main,,0,0,0,,but you've been way too loud during class lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:13.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I expect you to shape up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:16.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:17.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:21.08,Main,,0,0,0,,So I'm putting you in charge of\Ncleaning the science room after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:22.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:24.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to wipe the desks down, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:26.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:07.21,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not fair that it's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Takagi should be getting punished, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:12.48,Main,,0,0,0,,She's the one who's always teasing me during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:18.00,Main,,0,0,0,,But I guess the problem is\Nthat my reactions are too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.29,0:02:20.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's just get this over with and head--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:24.29,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing hiding in the closet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:28.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I was trying to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:30.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:33.25,Main,,0,0,0,,That was so worth having to waste time in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:36.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait. Lemme guess, you have to clean as punishment, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:40.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't we just get it over with?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:42.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:47.75,Main,,0,0,0,,So, I have a proposal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:49.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Before we start,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:51.58,Main,,0,0,0,,let's make a game out of cleaning, so it's more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:52.79,Main,,0,0,0,,A game?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:53.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:58.24,Main,,0,0,0,,How about we do rock-paper-scissors,\Nand the loser has to clean a quarter of the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:02:59.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:04.83,Main,,0,0,0,,That means if I win all four times,\NI won't have to clean anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Heh! Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.14,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:10.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Round one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:11.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll use rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:14.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Why's she telling me what she's gonna choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:17.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Rock. So if I go with paper, I'll win?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:19.54,Main,,0,0,0,,But she knows that, so--!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you I was going with rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:30.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.92,Main,,0,0,0,,You need to trust me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:33.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't be tricked twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:35.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll take her word for it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:36.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,And I'm not gonna tell you what I'm picking anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:43.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:47.33,Main,,0,0,0,,She's messing with me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishikata!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:53.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. Hey, Nakai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:54.83,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going' on in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:56.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You two just felt like hanging' out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:04:00.26,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I was loud in class,\Nso I have to clean the room as punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:03.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm. That's rough, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:04.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:08.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Me? I'm, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:10.25,Main,,0,0,0,,...just hanging' around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:11.45,Main,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:12.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:15.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's not get in their way, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:19.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:24.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Cool. See yah around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:25.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:27.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Good luck to yah, dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.29,Main,,0,0,0,,With this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:35.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's just get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:37.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:38.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,See yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:43.04,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, bet you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:44.41,Main,,0,0,0,,They're going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? They are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:48.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously? I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, I did notice them hanging\Nout a lot lately, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:54.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like they're trying to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:57.25,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just that they're both the kind\Nof people who wouldn't announce it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:58.66,Main,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:02.45,Main,,0,0,0,,He said he's hanging around, and she was with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:06.10,Main,,0,0,0,,But if you notice,\Nthey were on their way to the rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:08.42,Main,,0,0,0,,The... The rooftop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,And right about now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:13.00,Main,,0,0,0,,they're probably all alone up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:16.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Just the two of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:20.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You gonna clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh. Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:23.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:32.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Aww. Enjoying their time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,With each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Up there together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:37.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:39.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey. I finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:09.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:14.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:18.83,Main,,0,0,0,,How did I end up losing every time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:23.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that's finally done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:25.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go. It's getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.02,Main,,0,0,0,,So casual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:30.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope you learned your lesson\Nand won't tease me in class now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:31.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I could always just be more discreet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.79,Main,,0,0,0,,We're gonna get in trouble no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, if it happens, it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:40.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Not to mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:42.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't even told to clean in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:44.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:49.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Why am I the only one who gets in trouble all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:52.82,Main,,0,0,0,,So you're just here to mess with me, like usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.58,Main,,0,0,0,,There's that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:59.87,Main,,0,0,0,,...I wanted to enjoy my time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:04.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Enjoy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:08.00,Main,,0,0,0,,...your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:12.74,Main,,0,0,0,,And on that note,\Nyou're buying me juice on our way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.70,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.50,Main,,0,0,0,,The sun's killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:23.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:25.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm really thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:28.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,How about a competition and the loser buys drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:36.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:38.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I decide what we compete in then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Think I've got a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:42.22,Main,,0,0,0,,The high bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:47.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Whichever one of us can't do a\Nkickover on the high bar is the loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I just happened to try doing a\Nkickover on the high bar recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:56.66,Main,,0,0,0,,And bam! I was actually able to\Nfor the first time in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:08:00.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, I've been itching' for\Nmy chance to show Takagi up in a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:04.61,Main,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I wouldn't be all that\Nsurprised if she could do one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:06.91,Main,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:11.67,Main,,0,0,0,,You realize, I'm wearing a skirt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:13.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:16.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't flip over the bar wearing a skirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.08,Main,,0,0,0,,She's unable to compete!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:20.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:21.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:23.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I call dibs on going first, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:25.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:27.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Really? You want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:31.33,Main,,0,0,0,,However, I'd like to add one extra rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:33.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:34.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You're surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I am wearing a skirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:40.97,Main,,0,0,0,,So if you look at me on my turn, then you're the loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:55.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:58.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Your turn, show me what you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Did she really do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:03.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I have no way of knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Whatever, now's not the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:09.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I've gotta focus on the task at hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:15.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:18.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, we both were able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.00,Main,,0,0,0,,So what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.72,Main,,0,0,0,,One more time. Do over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.50,Main,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go first again, 'Kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:29.16,Main,,0,0,0,,No hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:30.75,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not a good sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:33.51,Main,,0,0,0,,She's either really confident or hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:36.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet she's not even doing a kickover.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:39.45,Main,,0,0,0,,She said I lose if I look during her turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:42.00,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's a different story if she's cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Today's the day that I finally beat her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:54.37,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:55.99,Main,,0,0,0,,She's actually doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Shorts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:10.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You can turn around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:16.12,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:17.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:19.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:26.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:28.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:30.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Though, I don't really feel like a winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:33.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Since you disqualified yourself and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:42.05,Main,,0,0,0,,If you had shorts on the whole time,\Nthen why didn't you let me watch you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:49.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:56.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:11:00.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to make sure you were\Nactually swinging over the bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:02.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:04.58,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:07.20,Main,,0,0,0,,So you thought I was cheating, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:10.75,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! No, I just... Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.83,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, what's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:34.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you always picking on me, day in and day out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:40.00,Main,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:43.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ba-dump!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:51.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Be straight. You like being treated this way, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:54.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh... Squeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:55.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:58.08,Main,,0,0,0,,"You like being treated this way, don't you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:00.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh... Squeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:04.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}100% Unrequited Love{\i0} is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Pay attention, this part's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:18.70,Main,,0,0,0,,And you can bet it's gonna be on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:20.67,Main,,0,0,0,,So make sure you remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:37.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Morning. Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:43.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:45.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting you. I thought you were out sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:52.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Morning. You have a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:54.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:57.29,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:58.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:00.20,Main,,0,0,0,,No big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:01.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Nailed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:04.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:08.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet you just stayed up watching {\i1}100% Unrequited Love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:12.08,Main,,0,0,0,,How did she figure that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:13.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Squeal, squeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:16.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't say that so loud, it's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Funny, I only heard you screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You're right. Sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:25.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, that was really low, Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:28.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You're coughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:31.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:38.04,Main,,0,0,0,,She won't pull any punches even when I'm sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:38.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:42.48,Main,,0,0,0,,But luckily, I have the ultimate\Nplan to defeat her today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:46.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, what's a guy like him doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:47.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Him and his perfect hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:48.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I'm really mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:51.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give him a piece of my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:03.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:04.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Squeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:20.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I may have caught a cold, but it was worth\Nit for the invaluable knowledge I've gained!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, Takagi. Come at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:26.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Gimme your best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:29.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll counter it and make you blush!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:32.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Ni--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:46.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:48.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Whenever you're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:52.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:54.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:57.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. 'S nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:07.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:09.29,Main,,0,0,0,,She isn't making her move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:11.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't stay in this pose forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:14.62,Main,,0,0,0,,And my right hand's on my chin,\Nso I can't even take notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:18.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, what if she figured it out because of the pose?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:21.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it too obvious I've got a\Ncounter-trap ready to spring on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,One way to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:27.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Sit normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What's her deal today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:43.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:46.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Any other day, she'd have teased me three times by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Is she sick or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:50.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:58.75,Main,,0,0,0,,When she's quiet, she's really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:20.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I'm starting to second guess my plan here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:24.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Countering with "You're cute," when she\Nmesses with me might be embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:26.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Duh, of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:28.98,Main,,0,0,0,,How did I ever think I'd be able to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:32.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet it's because I'm sick,\Nand didn't get any sleep last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:33.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:34.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.25,0:16:36.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:39.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Your face is a little red.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:39.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:40.87,Main,,0,0,0,,And you look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure you're good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:45.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:46.58,Main,,0,0,0,,But you're getting even redder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:48.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you being so nice to me today, Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:52.62,Main,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:54.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm totally okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:54.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.58,Main,,0,0,0,,When I said I was feeling sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.66,Main,,0,0,0,,it was more like an excuse, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:02.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I really just woke up at like,\Neight-thirty, so that's why I was late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine! Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:05.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:09.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It's about time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:13.16,Main,,0,0,0,,So... I can tease you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:14.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:20.13,Main,,0,0,0,,And of course, she ended up making\Nfun of me more than usual that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:22.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Young love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:24.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Squeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Yukari, Sanae, what's with the snail's pace?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:27.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Power walk, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:30.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Why should I exert myself that much for a Popsicle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:32.87,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cus, it's the baked sweet potato flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:34.58,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a summer exclusive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:36.45,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a weird flavor for summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:38.54,Main,,0,0,0,,They're sold out of it everywhere that I've looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.66,Main,,0,0,0,,But I think this one snack store will have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:43.83,Main,,0,0,0,,So we gotta check before they sell out too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:47.16,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:50.98,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no point in taking a shortcut if\Nyou're gonna drag your feet the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:55.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I just noticed Takagi and\NNishikata are inside the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:58.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh hey. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Could it be that those two are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Mina, maybe we shouldn't get in their way--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:06.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:14.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Sha-bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:16.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Got my sweet potato pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:19.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.08,Main,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:27.84,Main,,0,0,0,,They're so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Lucky how?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:31.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, look at the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:32.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:33.70,Main,,0,0,0,,A guy and a girl together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:35.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:38.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:41.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:44.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me, it was your idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:52.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey. Why exactly are we following them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.41,Main,,0,0,0,,We live in the opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Shhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.95,Main,,0,0,0,,They're gonna notice us. Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Just tell me what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:03.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I dunno, like something's going on between them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:06.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! They've got a bike right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:08.75,Main,,0,0,0,,They should be riding it together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.87,Main,,0,0,0,,That is so romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:12.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Riding home together after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:14.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, but that's a tough decision, because you can
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:16.75,Main,,0,0,0,,spend a lot more time together if you walk instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you trade off every other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:21.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I have a bite of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:24.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. Yeah, but just one bite, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:26.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.45,Main,,0,0,0,,You wanna race somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you challenging me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:31.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.58,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll start once we turn that corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:35.45,Main,,0,0,0,,The first one to make it all the way to the shrine wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:37.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Okay, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:41.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Haha. She either has to ride her bike or pull it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:43.16,Main,,0,0,0,,With that flat tire, she'll lose either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:45.45,Main,,0,0,0,,You have way too wild an imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:48.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I guarantee you they're not talking about a race!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:50.24,Main,,0,0,0,,They're talking about something more intimate than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:52.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:19:59.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:02.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm up for us racing to the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:04.08,Main,,0,0,0,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:05.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.20,Main,,0,0,0,,They're gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:17.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Did they make it all the way to the shrine already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:19.00,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:22.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe they realized we were tailing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh, come on, let's go home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:29.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:33.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I say we buy more popsicles on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you let me have a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:38.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Just buy your own if you're gonna keep eating mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:46.12,Main,,0,0,0,,So close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:56.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah. Did we lose them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:02.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Any idea why they were following us in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:04.08,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:05.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:08.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it,\Nwe should have gone around that corner too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:11.04,Main,,0,0,0,,It would have been a lot easier to hide over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I hadn't thought about that, guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:16.66,Main,,0,0,0,,But I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:19.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you have preferred if we did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:22.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:24.00,Main,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:24.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:26.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:27.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I almost forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:29.57,Main,,0,0,0,,We're racing to the shrine, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Ready, set go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:36.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm calling' you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.45,0:21:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a false start, Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:14.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Tailing those two turned out to be kinda fun in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:17.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Taking' the long way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:19.95,Main,,0,0,0,,They probably did notice us following them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:22.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I better apologize to Takagi tomorrow.
